        "description": "The Walk Through The Music with Poznań Philharmonic Orchestra\n\n34 musicians and a world-class Conductor recorded live in the concert hall with ZYLIA 6 DoF Navigable Audio system. Walkthrough the stage and stand next to any artist. Download the 360-degrees demo for VR goggles and take this immersive journey home where you smoothly navigate through the scene and experience the sound from anyplace – close perspective, the backstage, or the audience. Notice how the sound changes while passing by the musicians.\n\nComments:\n“The border between the musician and audience was existing for ages. Once you pass this border you are entering a real musical world. This kind of experience is an experience I cannot describe. You have to fill it.\"\n\nRecordings: Poznań Philharmonic Orchestra conducted by Łukasz Borowicz (Principal Guest Conductor Poznań Philharmonic Orchestra).\n\nMusic: W. A. Mozart - \"The Marriage of Figaro\", the overture",
